TitleDeed - Class in cards
The Title Deed class describes the title deed card of a property, train station or utility site such as a Water Works.
TitleDeed(String, String, int, String, int, int[], int, int, Player, CanOwn) - Constructor for class cards.TitleDeed
The class constructor is what we use to create the title deed card and it takes a lot of arguments to the higher parent class of Card but also edits the class variables unique to the Title Deed card

This is used for Player objects to select a TitleDeed card to conduct an operation such as mortgaging that CanOwn object associated with the TitleDeed card or perhaps build on the site.
